00:09:48.100 --> 00:09:52.670 align:middle line:84%
all that we are, all that we
experience, all that we embody

00:09:52.670 --> 00:09:56.085 align:middle line:84%
is part of that greater
understanding of reality.

00:09:56.085 --> 00:09:58.460 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Well, and also
because we have taken that dive

00:09:58.460 --> 00:10:01.430 align:middle line:84%
into scientific materialism,
all the way down to the bottom

00:10:01.430 --> 00:10:02.360 align:middle line:90%
of that well.

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:06.320 align:middle line:84%
We need that language and the
common vernacular for people

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:08.684 align:middle line:90%
to trust what you're saying.

00:10:08.684 --> 00:10:10.100 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: That
is so important.

00:10:10.100 --> 00:10:13.070 align:middle line:84%
