up and showing up--

00:10:16.210 --> 00:10:19.430 align:middle line:84%
and Dustin, as well, DiPerna,
talks about cleaning up--

00:10:19.430 --> 00:10:23.570 align:middle line:84%
over these years through
the whole awakening process

00:10:23.570 --> 00:10:25.190 align:middle line:90%
and the shift of awareness.

