universe is finite and closed,

00:13:39.130 --> 00:13:43.240 align:middle line:84%
which is additional evidence
to what I'm saying in the book.

00:13:43.240 --> 00:13:47.000 align:middle line:84%
But our universe began not as a
big bang, because we think of--

00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:47.800 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: I agree.

00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:49.550 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: --big
