00:13:49.550 --> 00:13:50.350 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:13:50.350 --> 00:13:51.930 align:middle line:90%
You call it the big breath.

00:13:51.930 --> 00:13:52.762 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: I do.

00:13:52.762 --> 00:13:53.720 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: I love this.

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:55.660 align:middle line:84%
Now, share this with
us, and we'll go forward

00:13:55.660 --> 00:13:57.480 align:middle line:90%
into that other question later.

00:13:57.480 --> 00:14:00.630 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: OK, because the big
breath actually perhaps begins

00:14:00.630 --> 00:14:02.630 align:middle line:90%
to answer that earlier question.

00:14:02.630 --> 00:14:06.750 align:middle line:84%
Because instead of chaos,
it was exquisitely ordered

00:14:06.750 --> 00:14:07.990 align:middle line:90%
and fine-tuned.

00:14:07.990 --> 00:14:09.920 align:middle line:84%
So literally, as
the ancients said,

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:14.950 align:middle line:84%
