flowing and space expanding.

00:14:14.950 --> 00:14:20.110 align:middle line:84%
So everything is
interconnected in the most

00:14:20.110 --> 00:14:25.630 align:middle line:84%
exquisitely-balanced way that
literally enables our universe

00:14:25.630 --> 00:14:28.450 align:middle line:90%
to exist, but more so to evolve.

00:14:28.450 --> 00:14:32.740 align:middle line:84%
So from that beginning
simplicity, ever greater levels

00:14:32.740 --> 00:14:38.330 align:middle line:84%
of complexity and ever greater
levels of self-awareness

00:14:38.330 --> 00:14:44.560 align:middle line:84%
at these individuated
microcosmic levels, such as us,

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:48.250 align:middle line:84%
