was there at the beginning,

00:14:53.839 --> 00:14:54.880 align:middle line:90%
will be there at the end.

00:14:54.880 --> 00:14:56.410 align:middle line:90%
It's just changed form.

00:14:56.410 --> 00:14:57.760 align:middle line:90%
I hate to say it, Regina.

00:14:57.760 --> 00:15:02.540 align:middle line:84%
But you and I are both
13.8 billion years old.

00:15:02.540 --> 00:15:03.340 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:15:03.340 --> 00:15:04.600 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: --in that sense.

00:15:04.600 --> 00:15:05.400 align:middle line:90%
We are.

00:15:05.400 --> 00:15:08.410 align:middle line:84%
So we have a lineage
as human beings

00:15:08.410 --> 00:15:11.560 align:middle line:84%
