00:15:23.160 --> 00:15:27.820 align:middle line:84%
And then you have
the logos informing

00:15:27.820 --> 00:15:32.500 align:middle line:84%
the prima materia, the
primordial essence of matter,

00:15:32.500 --> 00:15:35.200 align:middle line:90%
to create everything.

00:15:35.200 --> 00:15:36.010 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: Yes.

00:15:36.010 --> 00:15:37.285 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: How does that work?

00:15:37.285 --> 00:15:39.160 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: Basically,
because first of all,

00:15:39.160 --> 00:15:44.360 align:middle line:84%
