So what is the space?

00:17:32.821 --> 00:17:35.555 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: The space is
consciousness, essentially.

00:17:35.555 --> 00:17:36.010 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes, exactly.

00:17:36.010 --> 00:17:37.676 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: The space
is consciousness.

00:17:37.676 --> 00:17:41.455 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's where the
