00:17:41.455 --> 00:17:42.790 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: Exactly.

00:17:42.790 --> 00:17:43.740 align:middle line:90%
It is.

00:17:43.740 --> 00:17:44.590 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It is the space.

00:17:44.590 --> 00:17:44.750 align:middle line:90%
It is, yes.

00:17:44.750 --> 00:17:45.550 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: It is.

00:17:45.550 --> 00:17:48.880 align:middle line:84%
Because your mind
and consciousness

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:52.030 align:middle line:84%
