black hole-- think of a sphere,

00:22:47.570 --> 00:22:50.610 align:middle line:84%
think of a black hole as a
sphere in the event horizon--

00:22:50.610 --> 00:22:52.970 align:middle line:84%
that all that
information-- garbled,

00:22:52.970 --> 00:22:54.980 align:middle line:90%
but all the information--

00:22:54.980 --> 00:22:57.630 align:middle line:90%
is held on that surface area.

00:22:57.630 --> 00:22:59.440 align:middle line:84%
Now, what cosmologists
have done is

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:02.750 align:middle line:84%
they've taken that example
and then extended it

00:23:02.750 --> 00:23:05.330 align:middle line:84%
to the whole of our
universe to suggest

00:23:05.330 --> 00:23:08.630 align:middle line:84%
that the whole of our
universe, essentially,

00:23:08.630 --> 00:23:13.205 align:middle line:84%
