as we sort of wake up

00:48:15.770 --> 00:48:18.710 align:middle line:84%
to this larger
understanding of reality,

00:48:18.710 --> 00:48:21.920 align:middle line:84%
we realize that the material
realm is just partial.

00:48:21.920 --> 00:48:25.430 align:middle line:84%
