experiencing itself

00:48:25.430 --> 00:48:28.380 align:middle line:84%
and learning and growing
and all the rest of it.

00:48:28.380 --> 00:48:31.580 align:middle line:84%
So I would not say that the
physical world isn't real--

00:48:31.580 --> 00:48:32.600 align:middle line:90%
it is real.

00:48:32.600 --> 00:48:36.260 align:middle line:84%
What isn't real, what
is truly an illusion,

