is the appearance of separation.

00:48:38.460 --> 00:48:39.260 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:48:39.260 --> 00:48:42.410 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: And yet separation
of the appearance of separation

00:48:42.410 --> 00:48:44.750 align:middle line:84%
is also how we learn
from each other.

00:48:44.750 --> 00:48:45.932 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Well, we have
to learn through some kind

00:48:45.932 --> 00:48:46.500 align:middle line:90%
of contrast.

00:48:46.500 --> 00:48:47.430 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: Exactly.

00:48:47.430 --> 00:48:48.230 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:48:48.230 --> 00:48:50.580 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: If there's
nothing but it and self,

00:48:50.580 --> 00:48:51.984 align:middle line:90%
how would we learn?

00:48:51.984 --> 00:48:54.400 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: I don't know that
we could or can't even have

00:48:54.400 --> 00:48:55.170 align:middle line:90%
a sense.

00:48:55.170 --> 00:48:55.970 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: No.

00:48:55.970 --> 00:48:58.530 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: So let's not sort
of say, oh, separations are--

00:48:58.530 --> 00:48:59.640 align:middle line:90%
it isn't.

00:48:59.640 --> 00:49:02.610 align:middle line:84%
It's when we get into
a mindset that that's

00:49:02.610 --> 00:49:05.940 align:middle line:84%
all there is and we
really are separate,

00:49:05.940 --> 00:49:09.450 align:middle line:84%
and to get that extreme
materialism so that we

00:49:09.450 --> 00:49:13.660 align:middle line:84%
forget the ultimate
unity and oneness

00:49:13.660 --> 00:49:17.580 align:middle line:84%
and think that the
separation is just the thing,

00:49:17.580 --> 00:49:20.280 align:middle line:84%
then we act from that
place of separation.

00:49:20.280 --> 00:49:23.710 align:middle line:84%
And so, when we
remember the unity,

00:49:23.710 --> 00:49:26.640 align:middle line:84%
but come from a place
of unity and diversity--

00:49:26.640 --> 00:49:31.410 align:middle line:84%
because unity and
consciousness loves diversity.

00:49:31.410 --> 00:49:33.900 align:middle line:84%
Because again, it's
the maximum opportunity

00:49:33.900 --> 00:49:37.830 align:middle line:84%
to experience and learn
and grow and evolve.

00:49:37.830 --> 00:49:40.140 align:middle line:84%
But it's when we mistake
that unity and diversity

00:49:40.140 --> 00:49:42.690 align:middle line:90%
for separation that's the issue.

00:49:42.690 --> 00:49:45.780 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's an interesting
kind of line to play.

00:49:45.780 --> 00:49:49.260 align:middle line:84%
Because on one level,
a lot of people,

00:49:49.260 --> 00:49:51.330 align:middle line:84%
and a lot of people
watching this interview,

00:49:51.330 --> 00:49:56.970 align:middle line:84%
are really looking to go
into the experience of unity,

00:49:56.970 --> 00:50:00.780 align:middle line:84%
of non-separation,
of non-duality

00:50:00.780 --> 00:50:04.290 align:middle line:84%
through meditative practices
and so forth, and visualize

00:50:04.290 --> 00:50:06.990 align:middle line:84%
being a drop in the
ocean that's merging

00:50:06.990 --> 00:50:09.870 align:middle line:84%
with all of the other
drops in the ocean.

00:50:09.870 --> 00:50:16.405 align:middle line:84%
And thus, also shunning our
material physical reality.

00:50:16.405 --> 00:50:17.280 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: Exactly.

00:50:17.280 --> 00:50:18.690 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: And we can't do that.

00:50:18.690 --> 00:50:20.760 align:middle line:84%
This is where we
learn, is through

00:50:20.760 --> 00:50:22.480 align:middle line:90%
the contrast in this reality.

00:50:22.480 --> 00:50:25.530 align:middle line:84%
So I'd love for you to tell
us, on a personal level, how

00:50:25.530 --> 00:50:30.720 align:middle line:84%
you utilize and bridge these
two processes and potentials

00:50:30.720 --> 00:50:34.830 align:middle line:90%
and also gifts of being human.

00:50:34.830 --> 00:50:36.507 align:middle line:84%
>> CURRIVAN: I
feel this is vital,

00:50:36.507 --> 00:50:37.840 align:middle line:90%
because you're absolutely right.

00:50:37.840 --> 00:50:41.850 align:middle line:84%
We've got one aspect in
our collective psyche

00:50:41.850 --> 00:50:44.310 align:middle line:84%
that is still in the
materialistic appearance

00:50:44.310 --> 00:50:46.350 align:middle line:90%
of separation.

00:50:46.350 --> 00:50:50.310 align:middle line:84%
We've got another growing
aspect of our psyche, which

00:50:50.310 --> 00:50:52.220 align:middle line:90%
is going in that inner sense.

00:50:52.220 --> 00:50:59.190 align:middle line:84%
And as we go within, we remember
that's our natural connectivity

00:50:59.190 --> 00:51:03.000 align:middle line:90%
with the nature of reality.

00:51:03.000 --> 00:51:05.070 align:middle line:84%
The danger, as well
as the opportunity

00:51:05.070 --> 00:51:09.270 align:middle line:84%
of that in a journey,
is that we pull away

00:51:09.270 --> 00:51:12.460 align:middle line:84%
from the ostensibly
outer journey.

00:51:12.460 --> 00:51:15.720 align:middle line:84%
And so for me, it's how do we
balance the inner and outer?

00:51:15.720 --> 00:51:18.090 align:middle line:84%
Realizing that they are
just different sides

00:51:18.090 --> 00:51:23.610 align:middle line:84%
of the same coin of
overall unified reality.

00:51:23.610 --> 00:51:25.620 align:middle line:10%
And both are vital--

00:51:25.620 --> 00:51:30.570 align:middle line:10%
remembering the oneness of the
ocean, but also appreciating

00:51:30.570 --> 00:51:33.750 align:middle line:10%
and honoring the
individuation of the droplet.

00:51:33.750 --> 00:51:34.560 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:51:34.560 --> 00:51:37.770 align:middle line:10%
>> CURRIVAN: And if we went
from a process of nothing is

00:51:37.770 --> 00:51:41.550 align:middle line:10%
accidental, everything is
meaningful and purposeful,

00:51:41.550 --> 00:51:47.050 align:middle line:10%
cosmic mind didn't co-create
the appearance of all of this,

00:51:47.050 --> 00:51:49.270 align:middle line:10%
just so that we could
go into a gray gloop.

00:51:49.270 --> 00:51:50.550 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:51:50.550 --> 00:51:52.850 align:middle line:84%
This is the way I
have always seen it.

00:51:52.850 --> 00:51:55.680 align:middle line:84%
We are still individuated
consciousness, even

00:51:55.680 --> 00:51:56.700 align:middle line:90%
within the ocean.

00:51:56.700 --> 00:51:59.430 align:middle line:84%
We retain our
individuation and integrity

00:51:59.430 --> 00:52:03.085 align:middle line:84%
of the uniqueness that is
our signature, energetically.

00:52:03.085 --> 00:52:03.960 align:middle line:90%
>> CURRIVAN: Exactly.

00:52:03.960 --> 00:52:07.770 align:middle line:84%
And that gives us meaning
and purpose, both as

00:52:07.770 --> 00:52:11.850 align:middle line:84%
that individuated
microcosmic co-creator

00:52:11.850 --> 00:52:14.160 align:middle line:84%
of the intelligence
of our universe

00:52:14.160 --> 00:52:16.740 align:middle line:84%
and the infinite
and eternal cosmos.

00:52:16.740 --> 00:52:21.380 align:middle line:84%
And it also supports and
nurtures our remembering

00:52:21.380 --> 00:52:23.820 align:middle line:90%
of that ultimate unity.

00:52:23.820 --> 00:52:25.800 align:middle line:84%
So it's very much,
how do we turn

00:52:25.800 --> 00:52:31.860 align:middle line:84%
from the collective perspective
of just material separation,

00:52:31.860 --> 00:52:34.420 align:middle line:84%
