look the other way?

00:52:34.420 --> 00:52:37.650 align:middle line:84%
And we, instead of coming
from materialistic separation,

00:52:37.650 --> 00:52:39.660 align:middle line:84%
we come from unity,
but expressed

00:52:39.660 --> 00:52:43.094 align:middle line:84%
through the most incredible
abundance of diversity.

00:52:43.094 --> 00:52:44.010 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Absolutely.

00:52:44.010 --> 00:52:49.960 align:middle line:84%
Because it is about bringing
harmony between self and other,

00:52:49.960 --> 00:52:55.500 align:middle line:84%
that is the ultimate joy and
should be the ultimate goal

00:52:55.500 --> 00:52:57.820 align:middle line:90%
